title: Leave Spring Alone [Puzzle, Eng, 2018]
description:
Singular KKI game, where deft tactics are the key to a successful passage. Create your deck and use it to defeat your opponents.  But be very careful when choosing cards for the deck, because to win you need to pick the best hand. The game offers a good challenge, and you’ll need to best the four that already exist.
The once united people split into two opposing camps. The first lived in harmony with nature, and the second chose technological progress as the means for existence. After hundreds of years, technological development has reached an unthinkable level and the planet has become a bit overcrowded. Then they went to war on the lands inhabited by savages. According to their plan, a blitz attack and capture were supposed to take place within a few days, but is everything ever as simple as it sounds?

System:

ОС: Windows 7 +
CPU: 1.6 GHz
RAM: 256 mb
VRAM: 128 mb
HDD: 73 mb
